data.title: Jason Terry
data.meta_description: Dallas’ point guard starts the new season with something to prove – the Mavericks brought the league’s best record into the playoffs last season, only to get bounced by the Warriors in the first round. Terry looks to lead the Mavericks’ “Season of revenge” while also leading the league in sock thickness.
data.text:
Brand: NBA

Genre: Sports

Product Type: Action Figure

Series: NBA Series 13

Dallas’ point guard starts the new season with something to prove – the Mavericks brought the league’s best record into the playoffs last season, only to get bounced by the Warriors in the first round. Terry looks to lead the Mavericks’ “Season of revenge” while also leading the league in sock thickness.
